HEADWORD: Lamia
<hw>La"mi*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <fld>(Class. Myth.)</fld> <def>A monster capable of assuming
